{"tid":1585012,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[強烈建議]真料流料膠po留番俾時事台，行動/資訊po去政事台","createTime":"2019-09-21T11:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T12:00:05.000Z","uid":52817,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fff90275a79db9d2cafcfe882be4e4890d057ae0","tid":1585012,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:54:02.000Z","msg":"pt form<br />\n1.時事台太多po，根本膠po有用po都推唔起，推得起=抽中六合彩<br />\n2.行動/資訊po有特殊性，例如電筒po/防具po，必須手動置頂<br />\n3.政事台po比較少，容易置頂。<br />\n<br />\n4.建議所有行動/資訊po 除左時事台，開多個copy去政事台，政事台唔需要特別推。<br />\n5.建議大家唔好睇死一個時事台，得閒睇埋政事台。"},{"pid":"04df6818697622b234b7a8ff19930ed19d21181e","tid":1585012,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:54:25.000Z","msg":"[行動又無人理？] 全球最大親子抗爭活動上線啦！ <strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">#birdfoldingchallenge</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584614</a><br />\n摺一隻紙鳥，影相，放上Facebook / Twitter / Instagram，並加上hashtag #birdfoldingchallenge #929globalmarch #929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism，copy呢段文字再tag 5個朋友，就完成！</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYhkXcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYhkXcO.jpg&h=9b11593e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b726fa30ec4e991cd8dc1e0d607ad2aae0ca571e","tid":1585012,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:56:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4dd15a99aa83a8f91c65b6b9e8f940aace4ade35","tid":1585012,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:59:27.000Z","msg":"行動po去活動台啦"},{"pid":"c626b50069f54547f4a8b60f5e4d53e1a38799cc","tid":1585012,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b726fa30ec4e991cd8dc1e0d607ad2aae0ca571e","tid":1585012,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:56:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src